#x27;#e0e0e0&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">border_color:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\"># body background, default &#x27;#f5f7fa&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">background:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\"># Sidebar background (when opened), default to accent_color</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">sidebar_background:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\"># Card background, default &#x27;#fff&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">card_background:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\"># Maximum width of content</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">content_width:</span> <span class=\"number\">1400</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\"># Fonts</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">font:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\"># Url of font css file</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\"># Below is a font set containing Baloo Bhaijaan, Josefin Sans, Montserrat and Inconsolata from Google Fonts.</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">url:</span> <span class=\"string\">//fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Baloo+Bhaijaan|Inconsolata|Josefin+Sans|Montserrat</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\"># Base font which applied to body</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">base:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;&#x27;Josefin Sans&#x27;, &#x27;PingFang SC&#x27;&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\"># Sidebar author font, fallback to `base`</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">logo:</span> <s